      "# Valuation Assumptions Interview",
      "",
      "The interview uses discounted cash flow and 现金流折现 to translate future benefits into today's value.",
      "",
      "## Assumptions",
      "",
      "估值假设访谈 separates operating forecasts, discount rate, and terminal growth. ",
      "",
      "```text",
      "present_value = cash_flow / (1 + rate) ** year",
      "```",
      "",
      "## Aliases",
      "",
      "DCF, present-value model, and 折现现金流法 are equivalent labels in this corpus.",
      "",
      "## Limits",
      "",
      "A valuation range is more honest than a single unsupported target."
    ],
